column16: Jordan Schafer pops out to third baseman Gordon Beckham.
Paulo Orlando lines out softly to second baseman Micah Johnson.
Eric Hosmer grounds into a double play, first baseman Jose Abreu to shortstop Alexei Ramirez to first baseman Jose Abreu.   Lorenzo Cain out at 2nd.
Lorenzo Cain singles on a ground ball to right fielder Avisail Garcia.   Mike Moustakas to 2nd.
Mike Moustakas pops into a force out, third baseman Gordon Beckham to second baseman Carlos Sanchez.   Alcides Escobar out at 2nd.    Mike Moustakas to 1st.
Alcides Escobar singles on a line drive to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
